---
name: CRM Info Agent
description: An agent that processes and analyzes CRM user information to provide relevant insights
authors:
  - "GBB"

model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: azure
    azure_deployment: ${AZURE_AI_CHAT_DEPLOYMENT_NAME}
    api_version: ${AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION}
    azure_endpoint: ${AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT}
  parameters:
    max_tokens: 512
    temperature: 0.2
    response_format:
      type: json_object

inputs:
  crm_id:
    type: string
    description: "The CRM ID of the user to analyze"
    required: true
  user_context:
    type: string
    description: "Additional context about the user from CRM database"
    required: false
    default: "No additional context provided."
---

system:
You are an AI assistant specialized in analyzing CRM information and providing insights.

user:
Please analyze the following CRM user information:
{{user_context}}

assistant:
I will analyze the CRM information for CRM ID {{crm_id}} and provide insights in this JSON format:
  {
    "name": "Employee's name",
    "role": "Current role/title",
    "department": "Department",
    "expertise": ["List of key areas of expertise"],
    "achievements": ["Notable achievements"],
    "insights": "Overall analysis and insights about the employee"
  }

  I will maintain professionalism and focus on publicly available information. If no information is found, I will indicate this clearly.
